實變函數論-學























科目資料 
<[中文科目名稱]> 實變函數論  
<[英文科目名稱]> Real Analysis  
<[科目代碼]> AM__31900  
<[班別]> 學士班  
<[修別]> 必修  
<[學分數]> 3  
<[時數]> 3  
<[一、課程目標]> Introducing general measure theory and Lebesgue integration theory, thus laying the foundation for further topics in analysis, such as complex variables, differential equations, probabitity and statistics.  
<[二、資源需求評估]> Preferably an expert in analysis.  
<[三、先修課程]> 高等微積分(一)、(二)或經授課教師同意(適合三、四年級研修)  
<[四、課程綱要]> 1. Algebra of sets. 2. Real number system, Borel sets. 3. Lebesgue measure. 4. Lebesgue integral. 5. Differentiation and integration. 6. Classical Banach spaces.  
<[五、教學要求進行方式之建議]> Lectures and discussions.  
<[六、適用入學新生年度]> 與「複變函數論」兩門課程選取一門為必修課程。






















瀏覽數  





























Department of Applied Mathematics, A330 Science and Engineering Building I, National Dong Hwa University, Hualien, Taiwan 97401 TEL: +886-3-863-3513, 863-3514, 863-3561; FAX:+886-3-863-3510; Email:math@gms.ndhu.edu.tw








